snippet: A federal appeals court decided Thursday to unseal two dozen documents in a secret investigation into whether Gov. Scott Walker's campaign illegally coordinated with conservative groups in 2012....

headline.print_headline: Court to Unseal Some Files in Probe of Gov. Walker
headline.main: Court to Unseal Some Files in Probe of Gov. Walker

lead_paragraph: A federal appeals court decided Thursday to unseal two dozen documents in a secret investigation into whether Gov. Scott Walker's campaign illegally coordinated with conservative groups in 2012.
